<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بِهِ، وَإِنْ أُقِيمَتْ عَلَيْهِ بَيِّنَةٌ. <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَيُرْجَعُ فِيمَا ذُكِرَ إِلَى مُصْطَلَحَاتِ <span class="c2">(تَرْجِيحٍ، وَوَكَالَةٍ، وَكَفَالَةٍ، وَوِصَايَةٍ، وَوَصِيَّةٍ، وَوَقْفٍ)</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَوْزَانٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> مَقَادِيرَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
